  "detailed_description": "A person impersonating a member of an underground research institute with the aim of destroying all members of the research team. You will choose between becoming a member of team or impostor. As a member, find and detect the fake with the clues provided by the members. As an impostor, find the opportunity and destroy all members to win.<br><br>Peopel : <br>Win by finding the impostor .<br>Vote those with suspicious behavior to find out the impostor.<br>Complete all quests to win.<br><br>Murder :<br>Kill another people to win game.<br>Use destructive tricks to cause chaos and split the crew.<br>Destroy the system to cause chaos to find opportunities to kill others.<br>You will win when only have you and one person survive.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416340/extras/8b8f8e375c6d4afaa4038fb99a794709.poster.avif?t=1605779885\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416340/extras/8b8f8e375c6d4afaa4038fb99a794709.webm?t=1605779885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416340/extras/8b8f8e375c6d4afaa4038fb99a794709.mp4?t=1605779885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
